<aside>
<h2> How to develop a Healthy Eating Pattern </h2>
<p>You can devolop a healthy eating pattern by:</p>

	<ul class="mid2">
		<li class="tomato">Eating more vegetables and fruits</li>
		<li class="tomato">dark green such as broccoli and bok choy</li>
		<li class="tomato">orange such as carrots</li>
		<li class="tomato">Selecting whole grain varieties of grain foods</li>
		<li class="wheat">whole grain pasta</li>
		<li class="wheat">whole grain bread</li>
		<li class="wheat">whole oats or oatmeal</li>
		<li class="wheat">whole grain brown or wild rice</li>
		<li class="tomato">Replacing meats higher in saturated fat with leaner varieties</li>
		<li class="tomato">Replacing some of the meat in your meals with plant-based protein foods</li>
		<li class="tomato">Limiting highly processed foods</li>
	</ul>
</aside>
</section>

	<h2>Limit highly processed foods</h2>
	<p>Highly processed foods are processed or prepared foods and drinks that add excess sodium, sugars or saturated fat to the diets of Canadians.</p>
	
		<ul><em class="italic1">How to limit highly processed foods</em>
			<li>replace sugary drinks with water</li>
			<li>choose healthier menu options when eating out</li>
			<li>make homemade versions of your favourite highly processed foods</li>
		</ul>

		<ul><em class="italic1">Highly Processed Foods include</em>
			<li>sugary drinks</li>
			<li>syrups and jams</li>
			<li>chocolate and candies</li>
			<li>potato chips and pretzels</li>
			<li>sauces, dressings and gravies</li>
			<li>ice cream and frozen desserts</li>
			<li>fast foods like French fries and burgers</li>
		</ul>
<h3>Make Water your drink of choice</h3>
<p>You can<span style="color:#F97B22"><em>add fruits and herbs</em></span> to your hot or cold water for flavour.</p>

		<ul>
			<li>5 ways to add flavour to your water
				<ol type="a">
					<li>blackberries + mint</li>
					<li>raspberries + cucumber</li>
					<li>strawberries + fresh basil</li>
					<li>chopped apples + a cinnamon stick</li>
					<li>pear slices + a drop of vanilla extract</li>
				</ol>
			</li>
			<li class="check1"> If you like some fizz in your drink, try carbonated water</li>
			<li>Choose drinks that have little to no added sodium, sugars or saturated fat</li>
		</ul>
		
